434
00:44:38,139 --> 00:44:40,139
[SPEAKER_00] Slijediti u to, da, da.

435
00:44:40,139 --> 00:44:43,139
[SPEAKER_01] I sve je to, bitan je taj authority, jel?

436
00:44:43,139 --> 00:44:49,139
